# =============================================================================
# positivum — Retired prefix predicate; use value > 0.
# =============================================================================
#
# What this teaches:
#   • Retired syntax — This prefix predicate predates the modern infix `value > 0` pattern.
#   • Migration awareness — Understand how to translate old `positivum value` to `value > 0`.
#
# Common mistakes:
#   • Writing `positivum value` — the prefix predicate is retired; use `value > 0` instead.
